and Frisius, Thomas
and Ga{\v{s}}parac, Goran
and Giorgi, Filippo
and Goergen, Klaus
and Haugen, Jan Erik
and Hodnebrog, {\O}ivind
and Kartsios, Stergios
and Katragkou, Eleni
and Kendon, Elizabeth J.
and Keuler, Klaus
and Lavin-Gullon, Alvaro
and Lenderink, Geert
and Leutwyler, David
and Lorenz, Torge
and Maraun, Douglas
and Mercogliano, Paola
and Milovac, Josipa
and Panitz, Hans-Juergen
and Raffa, Mario
